@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(v2) * 0.75)
    v1 = wp.cos((0.86 + v1))
    v1 = (v1 * wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.73)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.14) + ((v1 + 0.55 * v2 + 0.53) * (v2 + 0.16 + v2 + 0.90)))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = (0.60 / v2)
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.abs(0.25)
    data[tid] = v0
